item.title: Essence CCDD Categories
item.description: name: essence_ccdd fullname: Essence CCDD Categories Trends description: >This template generates a trend report of Chief Complaint and Discharge Diagnosis (CCDD) Categories between the MMWR weeks containing the dates you choose. You are able to select as many of the CCDD Categories as you would like to generate this report and are able to control for data quality using the Average Weekly DDI% and CoV(HasBeenE) filters. Original Code By: Kelly Carey.
